 <p>Jather BlazingSoul<Br>35th and climbing wizard of E'ci<Br><a target="new" href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=293498>My_Magelo</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaerimusshadowborn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aerimus Shadowborn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/22/02 9:43:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=82.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: On the manaburn thing..</span><hr size=1> Why would it be horrible?  On blue servers you use your gear to level quicker and show off and thus the suggestions outlined wouldn't be apropriate but pvp is of primary importance on red servers.<br>
<br>
