<br>
Thus the well off high lvl player would be forced to equip his char in a manner more fitting for his lvl and compete on a more lvl playing field. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=seven>Seven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/28/02 9:25:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=82.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re</span><hr size=1> thus<br>
