Loyal Member of Giliath Lang</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/usollaiel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sollaiel</A> at: 7/29/02 7:58:49 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaerimusshadowborn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aerimus Shadowborn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/29/02 11:39:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=82.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> Why does it follow that resists should be lowered to compensate for the fact that spell dmg is reduced?<br>
